// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2505 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 2f606de8-1f34-505f-830c-3b2d0094b0e9

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
